        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258285/8500_258285_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "And in that of another,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258285_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258285/8500_258285_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "When she saw him, with the King standing before him, she rose and kissing him, gave him joy of the Sultanate and wished him and his sire length of life and victory over their foes.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258285_000009_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258285/8500_258285_000009_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "He sat with her and rested till the hour of mid afternoon prayer, when he took horse and repaired, with the Emirs before him, to the Maydan plain, where he played at arms with his father and his lords, till night fall, when he returned to the palace, preceded by all the folk.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258285_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258285/8500_258285_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "When it was the Seven Hundred and Forty fourth Night,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258286_000004_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258286/8500_258286_000004_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "When it was the Seven Hundred and Forty fifth Night,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258286_000005_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258286/8500_258286_000005_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "So name thou not the girl to thy son, till we demand her in marriage of her father.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258286_000005_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258286/8500_258286_000005_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "If he favour us with his assent, we will praise Allah Almighty; and if he refuse us and will not give her to thy son to wife, we will say no more about it and seek another match.\" Answered Julnar, \"Right is thy rede;\" and they parleyed no more: but Badr passed the night with a heart on fire with passion for Princess Jauharah.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258286_000005_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258286/8500_258286_000005_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "Now when it was morning, the King and his uncle went to the Hammam bath and washed, after which they came forth and drank wine and the servants set food before them, whereof they and Julnar ate their sufficiency, and washed their hands.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258286_000005_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258286/8500_258286_000005_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "Then Salih rose and said to his nephew and sister, \"With your leave, I would fain go to my mother and my folk for I have been with you some days and their hearts are troubled with awaiting me.\" But Badr Basim said to him, \"Tarry with us this day;\" and he consented.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258286_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258286/8500_258286_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "Then he sighed and wept and lamented, reciting these verses also,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258286_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258286/8500_258286_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "When Salih heard what his nephew said, he smote hand upon hand and said, \"There is no god but the God!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258286_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258286/8500_258286_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "Mohammed is the Apostle of God and there is no Majesty and there is no Might save in Allah, the Glorious, the Great!\" adding, \"O my son, heardest thou what passed between me and thy mother respecting Princess Jauharah?\" Replied Badr Basim, \"Yes, O my uncle, and I fell in love with her by hearsay through what I heard you say.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258286_000009_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258286/8500_258286_000009_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "Indeed, I fear to take thee and go without her leave, lest she be wroth with me; and verily the right would be on her side, for I should be the cause of her separation from us.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258286_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258286/8500_258286_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "When it was the Seven Hundred and Forty sixth Night,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258286_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258286/8500_258286_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "She said, It hath reached me, O auspicious King, that Badr Basim and his uncle, after diving into the deep, fared on till they came to Salih's palace, where they found Badr Basim's grandmother, the mother of his mother, seated with her kinsfolk and, going in to them, kissed their hands.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258286_000011_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258286/8500_258286_000011_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "Wherefore I purpose to carry her father a gift of jacinths and jewels befitting his dignity, and demand her of him in marriage.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258286_000011_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258286/8500_258286_000011_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "But what bringeth thee to us?",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258286_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258286/8500_258286_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "When it was the Seven Hundred and Forty seventh Night,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258286_000013_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258286/8500_258286_000013_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "Tell me thy tale and acquaint me with thy requirement.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258286_000013_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258286/8500_258286_000013_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "And these when they saw Salih come running out of the palace (they having been sent by his mother to his succour), questioned him and he told them what was to do; whereupon they knew that the King was a fool and violent tempered to boot.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258287_000000_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258287/8500_258287_000000_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "When it was the Seven Hundred and Forty eighth Night,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258287_000001_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258287/8500_258287_000001_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "So she fled forth the palace to a certain island, and climbing up into a high tree, hid herself in its summit.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258287_000001_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258287/8500_258287_000001_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "Now when the two parties came to blows, some of King Al Samandal's pages fled and Badr Basim meeting them, questioned them of their case and they told him what had happened.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258287_000001_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258287/8500_258287_000001_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "As he lay down, he raised his eyes to the tree and they met the eyes of the Princess.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258287_000001_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258287/8500_258287_000001_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "So he looked at her and seeing her to be like the moon rising in the East, cried, \"Glory to Him who fashioned yonder perfect form, Him who is the Creator of all things and who over all things is Almighty!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258287_000001_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258287/8500_258287_000001_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "Glory to the Great God, the Maker, the Shaper and Fashioner!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258287_000001_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258287/8500_258287_000001_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "By Allah, if my presentiments be true, this is Jauharah, daughter of King Al Samandal!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258287_000001_000010",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258287/8500_258287_000001_000010.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "As for me, I have quitted my kingdom for thy sake, and our meeting here is the rarest coincidence.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258287_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258287/8500_258287_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "When it was the Seven Hundred and Forty ninth Night,",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258287_000003_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258287/8500_258287_000003_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "Allah never requite him with good!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258287_000003_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8500/258287/8500_258287_000003_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8500",
        "content": "How unlucky was his coming to us; for all this trouble is due to his hard headedness!",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8500_258287_000003_000016",
